data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath colonial in Euclid.   This home offers a large family room with fireplace, dining room, eat in kitchen, 1/2 bath and a sunroom on the first floor.   3 spacious bedrooms on the second floor with an updated full bathroom.  The basement is partially finished.    The home was recently updated in 2016.  Attached, single car garage, private back yard with an above ground pool that does stay.   Beautiful large front yard.
